{"tid":1243582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【開定先】　無論咩崗位都好，為６２１準備","createTime":"2019-06-19T13:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:21:29.000Z","uid":258197,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"36095f678e1be8c6dbfaf237c9bbd67fac3af74e","tid":1243582,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"無論你係邊一派，發唔發夢都黎睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n勇武既手足們：<br />\n&mdash;出面已經好多好有用既Post，請準備好晒保護自己<br />\n&mdash;收拾心情好好休息準備６２１<br />\n&mdash;發過夢既手足應該知道信號係會收得勁差，信任夢境中既同伴們<br />\n&mdash;自行評估收到既消息可信性<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非既手足們：<br />\n&mdash;用自己既方式盡力支援啦（無論物資上／一齊發夢但後排幫義士壯膽）<br />\n&mdash;當日任何消息請Fact check（好重要！）先至好轉發／通報比夢境中前線手足聽<br />\n&mdash;承上，通訊用依度開Post既話係夢入面既手足可能好難收到，請開Post之餘並用自己方式聯絡自己認識既係夢境入面既朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然都係啲好大路既野，但希望要保持警覺勿鬆懈，未嬴架我地<br />\n<br />\n不流血，不被捕，不篤灰，不割蓆，不分化<br />\n<br />\n加油<br />\n天祐香港"},{"pid":"95b7cbb1442df4d65cb97427439963f73e71b023","tid":1243582,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:51:14.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37df0fc0c5bf564919c2a9c1e806167e89499556","tid":1243582,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812140929de887a8627c325375dabb37246f2b72","tid":1243582,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0996149464fbe7e8ed2f389cbccced163a1746c7","tid":1243582,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603d6cf20e595ab487d09c266bfbd1b893155